  "instructions": [
    "In a blender or food processor, combine the red curry paste, coconut oil, lime juice, honey, soy sauce, rice vinegar, and spicy pepper flakes. Blend until smooth.",
    "Add the chopped cilantro and blend until well combined.",
    "Cut the cobnuts in half lengthwise and place them in a large bowl.",
    "Pour the blended curry paste mixture over the cobnuts and toss to coat.",
    "Season the cobnuts with salt and black pepper.",
    "Heat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread the cobnuts onto skewers, if using.",
    "Grill the cobnuts for 2-3 minutes per side, or until they are slightly charred and tender.",
    "Serve the satay hot with your favorite dipping sauce."
  ],
